'''救贖石洞'''（The Shrine of the Grotto of the Redemption）是位於[[美國|美國]][[愛荷華州|愛荷華州]][[西本德_(艾奥瓦州)|西本德]]的一個宗教場所。九個洞穴描繪了[[耶穌|耶穌]]的一生。該洞穴被認為是世界最大的人工洞穴<ref name="agilitynut">[http://www.agilitynut.com/h/redemption.html Grotto of the Redemption] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130605151218/http://www.agilitynut.com/h/redemption.html |date=2013-06-05 }}, agilitynut.com</ref>，集合了多種礦物<ref name="iowabeautiful">[http://www.iowabeautiful.com/northwest-iowa-tourism/131-grotto-redemption-west-bend-iowa.html Iowa Tourism / Northwest / Grotto Of The Redemption - West Bend, Iowa] {{Wayback|url=http://www.iowabeautiful.com/northwest-iowa-tourism/131-grotto-redemption-west-bend-iowa.html |date=20210412010711 }}, iowabeautiful.com</ref>。構成洞穴的礦物價值超過$4,308,000<ref name="csumc">[http://csumc.wisc.edu/newsletter/grottos.htm Grottos of the Midwest: Religion and Patriotism in Stone] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081007203155/http://csumc.wisc.edu/newsletter/grottos.htm |date=2008-10-07 }}, by Peyton Smith, csumc.wisc.edu</ref><ref>cited as over $4 million: [http://www.roadsideamerica.com/story/2083 Grotto of the Redemption, West Bend, Iowa] {{Wayback|url=http://www.roadsideamerica.com/story/2083 |date=20210811035506 }}, roadsideamerica.com</ref>。每年有超過10萬人參觀救贖石洞<ref name="iowabeautiful"/><ref>[http://www.essortment.com/all/westbendiowa_rswy.htm West Bend, Iowa: grotto of the redemption - West Bend, Iowa home to the Grotto of the Redemption a work of love and art depicting the life of Christ by Father Dobberstein] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303210524/http://www.essortment.com/all/westbendiowa_rswy.htm |date=2016-03-03 }}, essortment.com</ref><ref>[http://www.westbendgrotto.com/history/passing_the_torch.htm Passing the Torch]{{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090216021321/http://westbendgrotto.com/history/passing_the_torch.htm |date=2009-02-16 }}, westbendgrotto.com</ref>。
